17 years in & the Creamfields festival has grown in stature and quality to become the UK's premier biggest outdoor dance music festival. Last years festival won best Dance Festival at the UK Festival Awards & this year's the fastest selling Creamfields to date & is on course for it's 5th consecutive sell out. Album highlights include UK 5 x no 1's from Martin Garrix - Animals. And 3 x Top 10's from Avicii's co-produced Coldplay - A Sky Full of Stars, Klingande - Jubel, Clean Bandit - Extraordinary & Calvin Harris -Thinking About You. Plus future hits from Lilly Wood & Robin Schulz - Prayer In C & Hot Natured - Benediction.
